org.jemmy.dock

Annotation Type DefaultWrapper


  • @Target(value=METHOD)
@Documented
public @interface DefaultWrapper
    Putting this on a public static method allows to generate constructors which do not take parent as a parameter, taking whatever is coming from this method instead. An annotated method should take one parameter - class of the controls to by looked for and should return parent for that type.
    Author:
    shura
